`checksums/SHA256SUMS`. The publish orchestrator validates those files
before upload: final weights, checksum coverage, eval outputs, license
blobs, graph-dispatch reports, platform evidence, and the
`elizaos/eliza-1-{{ tier }}` destination must all match the bytes in
this repo.

